    "This was then aggregated into annotations of whether anthropomorphism is present.",
    "After the first round of annotation, there was a moderate agreement between annotators (Cohen's κ = 0.40).",
    "After discussing disagreements and re-annotating, we reached substantial agreement (Cohen's κ = 0.87).",
    "To include more sentences with extreme sentences, we also use a stratified set of 100 masked sentences based on A score quartile.",
    "For this set, we had high agreement after the first round of annotation, so we did not discuss disagreements or reannotate."
